high_descs: Turn right then head to the toilet left side
Pick up a candle on the tank
Turn right then put the candle on the shelf
Put the candle on the shelf
Turn right then go to the left side of the toilet
Pick up the  candle on the tank

Put the candle on the shelf

high_descs: Walk to the wall and turn right and walk forward to the toilet.
Pick up the farthest from you candle stick on the right.
Turn right and walk to the first white table on your right.
Place the candlestick on the table to the left of the three bottles.
Turn right and walk back to the toilet.
Pick up the candlestick on top of the toilet farthest on the right.
Turn right and walk to the first white to table on your right.
Place the candlestick on the table to the left of the first candlestick.
anns.task_desc: Place two candlesticks on the first white table closest to the toilet.

high_descs: Go forward and turn to the right to face the left side of the toilet.
Pick the candle to the right of the empty roll up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and face the white cabinet with the green cloth.
Put the candle down right of the green cloth.
Turn to the right and stand on the left side of the toilet.
Pick the candle on the right up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and face the white cabinet with the green cloth.
Put the candle down on the white cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on a cabinet.
